Attempt to query restricted annotations in GenePattern
Comments: The GenePattern expression data analysis workflows were tested and found to be secure. Attempting to analyze unauthorized expression data using grid services results in Local Error Unable to create GCT file: No data found from selection. Analyzing authorized expression data using grid services properly restricts by subject. Attempting to analyze unauthorized expression data using GenePattern modules displays a status of completed in caIntegrator but correctly shows an error in GenePattern. Analyzing authorized expression data using GenePattern modules correctly restricts by annotation, displaying Local Error Couldn't execute GenePattern analysis job: null, and correctly restricts by subject.
